com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-01.50.20-768x864.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-01.50.20-400x450.jpeg 400w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-01.50.20.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 910px) 100vw, 910px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0edf5c9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0edf5c9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43b4a29 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"43b4a29\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6338d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d6338d3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>What to Expect<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Morning Pick-Up:<br><\/b>Our driver will pick you up from your riad or hotel in Marrakech and take you on a scenic drive to the Ourika Valley. As you journey through picturesque landscapes, you\u2019ll see lush greenery, flowing rivers, and the majestic Atlas Mountains.<\/p>\n<p><b>Explore the Valley:<br><\/b>Upon arrival, you can stroll through the valley, visit traditional Berber villages, and take in the tranquil surroundings.<\/p>\n<p><b>Lunch Options:<br><\/b>Enjoy lunch at any restaurant you prefer near the riverbanks of the Ourika Valley. Many restaurants offer seating right next to the flowing river, providing a unique and relaxing dining experience with delicious Moroccan cuisine.<\/p>\n<p><b>Hike to the Waterfalls:<br><\/b>After lunch, you can go for a short hike with a local guide to visit the famous Ourika waterfalls. The walk offers beautiful views of nature and the chance to see the stunning cascade up close.<\/p>\n<p><b>Visit Setti Fatma:<br><\/b>End your day with a visit to Setti Fatma, the heart of the Ourika Valley. This charming village is known for its natural beauty, traditional Berber culture, and access to the valley&#8217;s iconic waterfalls.<\/p>\n<p><b>Additional Highlights:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Opportunity to visit a local cooperative where Berber women produce argan oil.<\/p>\n<p>Experience the simple and authentic Berber lifestyle.<\/p>\n<p><b>Return to Marrakech:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>After an unforgettable day, our driver will take you back to Marrakech in the late afternoon.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Private Trip to Ourika Valley \u200b Discover the serene beauty of the Ourika Valley, a refreshing getaway from the hustle and bustle of Marrakech. This private tour offers flexibility and comfort, letting you enjoy the valley at your own pace. What to Expect Morning Pick-Up:Our driver will pick you up from your riad or hotel [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11313,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11672","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11672","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11672"}],"version-history":[{"count":21,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11672\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12779,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11672\/revisions\/12779"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11313"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11672"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}